tyle=\"margin:0px;padding:8px 20px 50px\"><h3 style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;color:rgb(0,0,0);clear:both\"><p data-indent=\"0\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img0.tech2ipo.com/upload/img/article/2014/11/1415933293800.png\" _src=\"http://img0.tech2ipo.com/upload/img/article/2014/11/1415933293800.png\" class=\"\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">2014 年 10 月 31 日，注定是改变一切的一天。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">那一天，首期天使汇闪投 Speed Dating 在天使汇全球路演中心举行，改变了创投的玩法。那一天，8 个小时的时间，11 个项目，2 个项目获得了千万级意向，1 个获得了 700 万级意向，其余的 8 个项目也没有空手而归，分别获得了从 100~500 万元不等的投资。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">我们从未忘记，我们的目标是让好的项目与智慧的投资更快的相遇，而第一期闪投仅仅向这个目标迈出了一小步――当我们为这 11 个项目欢欣鼓舞的时候，有更多的项目和更多投资人正在期待着遇见彼此。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px\">为了能够帮助对项目进行深层次的挖掘，Speed Dating 1.1（第二期）将在本周六（2014 年 11 月 15 日）举行线下初选会！初选会将安排以下内容：</span></strong>\n</p>\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 14px;\">\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">天使汇业务流程讲解，教你如何使用天使汇平台</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">TECH2IPO/创见媒体沙龙，探讨创业者如何与媒体打交道</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">天使汇创投经理现场面试，通过初选的项目将入选第二期闪投 Speed Dating</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">《斯坦福创业课――创业中的反直觉》观看与交流</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">面试前准备（至少二选一）：</span>\n</p>\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 14px;\">\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">在天使汇上创建项目并上传 BP（商业计划书）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"list-style: disc; margin: 0px 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">产品原型或产品 Demo 可以在当天进行展示</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px;\">\n    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline